APIs
--- 

Get all movies: 

Request URL: /api/movies 
Method: GET 
Body: --
Response: [{movie}, {movie}]


Get single movie 

Request URL: /api/movies/{some unique identifier}
Method: GET 
Body: --
Response: movie 


Create a movie 

Request URL: /api/movies 
Method: POST 
Body: {movie}
Response: status: true / movie created 

Update a movie 
Request URL: /api/movies/{some unique id}
Method: PUT / PATCH 
Response: status: true / update movie object 


DELETE a movie 

Request URL: /api/movies/{some unique id}
Method: DELETE
Response: status: true / deleted movie object
